# RealtimeLinePlotter - Live Data Chart Generator

RealtimeLinePlotter plots incoming numerical data in real-time for demos, simulations, or monitoring.

## Features
- Real-time updates  
- Scrollable window  
- Clean display  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_RealtimeLinePlotter.git
cd 21_RealtimeLinePlotter
python visualize.py
